      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just so tired of everything. everything feels heavy lately. it used to be me looking after him, but now i'm the one with the constant appointments and the pills and the help needed just to get around. i look at my kids and i see how much they're struggling to keep up with me, and it just breaks my heart. i don't want to be a nuisance anymore.",
